title: June 2009 Primary Election for Governor Results, by Candidate, New Jersey
name: June 2009 Primary Election for Governor Results, by Candidate, New Jersey
description: This is a shapefile of primary election results in New Jersey for Governor by candidate in June of 2009. The data is at the county level and comes from The State of New Jersey Department of State. Data was uploaded into Geocommons as shp, dbf, and shx files.

author.source: The State of New Jersey Department of State
